      <title>亚洲股市小幅走高，美元在美国通胀报告公布前保持稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-13/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，在美国关键通胀报告发布之前，亚洲股市小幅走高，美元保持稳定，该报告可能有助于塑造美联储的利率前景并确定降息时机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-13/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 02:03:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于需求担忧抵消了中东风险，油价接近持平</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-near-flat-demand-worries-offset-middle-east-risk-2024-02-13/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，油价连续第二天几乎没有变化，因为美国潜在降息步伐的不确定性以及对燃料需求的影响抵消了对中东紧张局势可能扰乱供应的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-near-flat-demand-worries-offset-middle-east-risk-2024-02-13/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 01:38:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
